Romain Duris https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Romain_Duris 0 Romain Duris (French pronunciation: [ʁɔmɛ̃ dyʁis] (listen); born 28 May 1974) is a French actor, best known for his role in Cédric Klapisch's Spanish Apartment trilogy, which consists of L'Auberge Espagnole (2002), Russian Dolls (2005) and Chinese Puzzle (2013). He also appeared in the 2017 film All the Money in the World.
